### Component 1: Engine Core and Event Bus Architecture

The **Engine Core** provides centralized orchestration and lifecycle management for all subsystems. The **Event Bus Subsystem (EB-SUB)** enables asynchronous, decoupled communication between components.

**Novel Features:**
